{"tid":623424,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"世界cue后吳安儀連續3年參與桌球壇最高榮譽比賽","createTime":"2018-04-10T03:47:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-30T13:19:52.000Z","uid":32403,"like":122,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"7c8a36f8e5a61abb89a3ba6feca23cb2197fd1b5","tid":623424,"uid":32403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T03:47:13.000Z","msg":"七次香港傑出運動員 兩次星中之星<br />\n吳安儀連續三年出席桌球壇年度最大盛事 世錦賽 外圍賽<br />\n要由外圍賽打入正賽好簡單 連贏3場 就可以打入正賽 即係最後32強<br />\n而世界排名頭16 一早就分好晒種子 係正賽等緊外圍賽出線既球手<br />\n<br />\n吳安儀過往兩年成績<br />\n2016世錦賽外圍賽第一輪  Peter Lines 10 : 1  Ng On Yee<br />\n2017世界賽外圍賽第一輪  Nigel Bond 10 : 1  Ng On Yee<br />\n2018既對手已經出左 係Matthew Selt (現時世界排名57, 高峰排名21)<br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以支持安儀 今年贏多兩局<br />\n<br />\n順帶一提 因眼睛出現百幾粒黑點而被逼做手術休息幾個月既傅家俊宣佈復出<br />\n雖然手術後完全無改善 <br />\n但因為佢今次唔打會保唔住頭16 而且係咁大型比賽 所以點都會打<br />\n<br />\n今次亦都會係傅家俊第17次參加世錦賽<span style=\"color: red;\">正賽</span><br />\n最好成績 兩次4強 兩次8強 其中一次4強係前年 一次8強係上年 都係輸俾當屆冠軍<br />\n前年僅敗 上年被大炒<br />\n<br />\n然而 傅家俊 只有 四次香港傑出運動員 零次星中之星<br />\n香港體壇奧斯卡 wtf?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7f760ef122a53aa1f2c9b1ea0a460abc2858fcb","tid":623424,"uid":14497,"like":12,"dislike":25,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T03:54:51.000Z","msg":"有閪好似大哂"},{"pid":"450aad713c46f41f2064823fb6b84f684e6fa244","tid":623424,"uid":32403,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T03:55:02.000Z","msg":"屌 唔記得左講幾時開波<br />\n外圍賽聽日就會正式開始<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://livescores.worldsnookerdata.com/Sessions/Tournament/14004/betfred-world-championship-2018-qualifiers\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flivescores.worldsnookerdata.com%2FSessions%2FTournament%2F14004%2Fbetfred-world-championship-2018-qualifiers&d=xWAbz9ssH%2FWTMwmoULOGf5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=9576f7c2\" target=\"_blank\">http://livescores.worldsnookerdata.com/Sessions/Tournament/14004/betfred-world-championship-2018-qualifiers</a><br />\n<br />\n由於係打19局10勝制 所以會分兩節打<br />\n第一節打9局 第二節就分勝負<br />\n<br />\n安儀將會係聽日 <br />\n英國時間上午10點 (香港時間 下午5點) 打第一節<br />\n英國時間晚上7點 (香港時間 凌晨3點) 打決勝節"},{"pid":"21a9d09fedbd8cba2506f5abdc854b790b9702fe","tid":623424,"uid":32403,"like":12,"dislike":4,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"f7f760ef122a53aa1f2c9b1ea0a460abc2858fcb","tid":623424,"uid":14497,"like":12,"dislike":25,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T03:54:51.000Z","msg":"有閪好似大哂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T03:56:26.000Z","msg":"佢拎獎唔係佢既錯 係香港政府既錯 <br />\n香港桌球壇代表人物 一直都係傅家俊 <br />\n起碼係佢之後 到依家都未有另一個職業球手"},{"pid":"3a3b3955ec7e35f967674b80ed577d08d2f3d1f6","tid":623424,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T03:56:54.000Z","msg":"其實女子有冇特別操體能？伊雲斯都試過過到第一圈"},{"pid":"3cba33820f15887422fade94c3b6db608c697573","tid":623424,"uid":8883,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T03:57:26.000Z","msg":"但-6未好番照打會唔會惡化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73054df1eed050b901dfddebe10037a646a4f2d0","tid":623424,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T03:57:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實女子有冇特別操體能？伊雲斯都未試過過到第一圈</blockquote>"},{"pid":"b453fa2242f4bf79240edfc34fc742fe1b91a1db","tid":623424,"uid":1067,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T03:58:58.000Z","msg":"cue后依家仲會唔會坐巴士？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/10/115848_51437e891fee1ea31b052dc0ee96beed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F10%2F115848_51437e891fee1ea31b052dc0ee96beed.png&h=0a3f1d87&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"274bc385cbb4357eae84ae66a4f0fe9af3545b5e","tid":623424,"uid":66496,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T04:00:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>cue后依家仲會唔會坐巴士？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/10/11584